{"tid":1256671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中環海濱用地割讓解放軍 無人講？","createTime":"2019-06-25T06:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T07:08:00.000Z","uid":92611,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"71e9f87c27411d34ebfedc8abdcc5d9dd1de4132","tid":1256671,"uid":92611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:50:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/立會周三審議中環海濱用地割讓解放軍-保護海濱聯盟促廢除議案/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%89%E5%AF%A9%E8%AD%B0%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E6%B5%B7%E6%BF%B1%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%89%B2%E8%AE%93%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D-%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E6%B5%B7%E6%BF%B1%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E4%BF%83%E5%BB%A2%E9%99%A4%E8%AD%B0%E6%A1%88%2F&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443mmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=f8bf5aba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%89%E5%AF%A9%E8%AD%B0%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E6%B5%B7%E6%BF%B1%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%89%B2%E8%AE%93%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D-%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E6%B5%B7%E6%BF%B1%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E4%BF%83%E5%BB%A2%E9%99%A4%E8%AD%B0%E6%A1%88%2F&h=58eb47e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/立會周三審議中環海濱用地割讓解放軍-保護海濱聯盟促廢除議案/</a><br />\n<br />\n到時一有人係添馬集結示威 就出動海濱警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/06/20190614_PO_%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A_FB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F06%2F20190614_PO_%25E9%2580%259F%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%259A%258A_FB.jpg&h=f499246c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1464040_1_L_20190620170657.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1464040_1_L_20190620170657.jpg&h=2e4d221d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">立會周三審議中環海濱用地割讓解放軍</span><br />\n<br />\n中環海濱長廊一幅 0.3 公頃土地，被政府改劃為「軍事用地」。本周三（26日）立法會大會將審議相關的附屬法例，議會陣線朱凱迪和區諾軒提出多項修訂，包括是將附屬法例廢除等。保護海濱聯盟今日發出緊急呼籲，要求全體立法會議員支持廢除議案，避免將中環海濱「送中」。<br />\n<br />\n立法會星期三將會討論中區軍用碼頭相關的附屬法例，區諾軒將提出多項修訂要求廢除附屬法例。朱凱迪則提出將生效日期由本月底，推遲至明年、後年或2047年。<br />\n<br />\n保護海濱聯盟今日指，政府有關做法等同將中環海濱「送中」，指港人的海濱公共空間慘變成軍事用地，是嚴重損害公眾利益。聯盟呼籲全體立法會議員支持廢除議案，不要強行通過惡法、製造社會矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n2014 年城規會決定將中環海濱長廊核心地段之 150 米長、3,000 平方米面積的土地劃作「軍事用途」。分區計劃大綱圖於今年 1 月已提交予特首林鄭月娥，她同意了計劃草案並於 2 月 1 日刊憲關於批准計劃草案的通知。<br />\n<br />\n今年 2 月，立法會議員朱凱廸與中環海濱關注組名名成員到中環海濱長廊集會，抗議政府長廊用地劃作軍事用途，供駐港解放軍使用。朱凱廸批評，政府不單不取回閒置軍事用地作公共用途，更將現有公共空間改劃為軍事用地，要求政府立即開放該處用地予公眾，只有解放軍需要停泊船隻時才暫時圍封。<br />\n<br />\n今年4月保安局亦在立法會保安事務委員會提交文件，指政府計劃於本立法年度內，提交法例修訂建議予立法會，並於立法工作完成後，將碼頭正式移交予駐軍。"},{"pid":"8c7ce09022f878abd45fe8774a79f18e3cac5a9e","tid":1256671,"uid":262822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:52:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca43de3568f76d71c91d0605914c1350de621c59","tid":1256671,"uid":244876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T07:00:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1256651/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1256651/page/1</a><br />\n如果你預左打長久戰，歡迎睇下(長文)<br />\n以下係某絲打諗左好耐既長文，求大家認真睇落去。"},{"pid":"1b36859c25931a14a1011e4ab87b53cd7220f798","tid":1256671,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T07:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5d74bcfceb7828e65119c8fef900384224746d","tid":1256671,"uid":125453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T07:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xNvet5B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxNvet5B.png&h=ac36f72f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hwdonqC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhwdonqC.jpg&h=4a214cc9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}